## üìÅ Project Structure (Simplified)

* `app/` ‚Äî Next.js App Router (routes, layouts, APIs)
  * `api/jobs/` ‚Äî Job CRUD and search endpoints
  * `dashboard/` ‚Äî User job management dashboard
