## üîå API Endpoints

### Jobs

* `GET /api/jobs` ‚Äî List all jobs
* `POST /api/jobs` ‚Äî Create a new job (authenticated)
* `GET /api/jobs/[id]` ‚Äî Get a specific job
* `PUT /api/jobs/[id]` ‚Äî Update a job (owner/admin only)
* `DELETE /api/jobs/[id]` ‚Äî Delete a job (owner/admin only)
* `GET /api/jobs/search?q=query` ‚Äî Search jobs by keyword

### Authentication

* `POST /api/auth/signup` ‚Äî Register a new user
* `POST /api/auth/signin` ‚Äî Sign in a user
* `POST /api/auth/signout` ‚Äî Sign out a user

